				<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>In this lesson I’ve just released I’m going to show you an epic bass lick you can use over *ANY* chord!</p>
<p>Seriously... whatever groove you’re playing, whatever chord you’re playing over, you can use this lick - but the secret is the placement and timing of how you use it.</p>
<p>As always, I'd love to hear from you guys in the comments!</p>
<p>See you in the shed...</p>
<p>Scott :)</p>
<p>PS. I actually stole this lick from a bass player you’ll most likely have heard 100’s if not 1000’s of times before (he’s one of the most recorded bass players of all time!) - I’ll tell you all about it in this new lesson.</p>
