		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://scottsbasslessons.com/?p=4660</guid>
		<description><![CDATA[<p>WARNING!... In this bass lesson I'm going to show you a 'KILLER AWESOMESAUCE LICK' to demonstrate how to use the different fingerings of each arpeggio and how this will help you to play over the entire fingerboard... LIKE A BAD...</p>
<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="http://www.scottsbasslessons.com/licks/stuck-in-one-area-of-the-fingerboard-watch-this.html">Stuck in one area of the fingerboard? Watch this! (L#91)</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="http://www.scottsbasslessons.com">Online Bass Lessons</a>.</p>
